                <p class="text-slate-600">The heavily developed Etobicoke Creek watershed regularly exceeds capacity during storms and spring melt, causing dramatic water table rises and basement flooding in Heart Lake, Bramalea, and Springdale neighborhoods.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-cyan-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
